{"word":"G4374 - προσφέρω - prosphérō - pros-fer'-o - Bring","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">προσφέρω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">prosphérō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">pros-fer'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Bring</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - கொடு, கொண்டுவா, செலுத்து, ஒப்புவி"},{"paragraph":"1. to bring to, lead to"},{"paragraph":"2. to attack, assail"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G4314 - πρός - prós - pros/4314\">G4314</a> and <a href=\"#/G5342 - φέρω - phérō - fer'-o/5342\">G5342</a> (including its alternate); to <i>bear towards</i>, that is, <i>lead to</i>, <i>tender</i> (especially to God), <i>treat:</i> - bring (to, unto), deal with, do, offer (unto, up), present unto, put to.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G1308/1308\">G1308</a>, <a href=\"#/G1313/1313\">G1313</a>, <a href=\"#/G2018/2018\">G2018</a>, <a href=\"#/G399/399\">G399</a>, <a href=\"#/G4374/4374\">G4374</a>, <a href=\"#/G4376/4376\">G4376</a>, <a href=\"#/G4851/4851\">G4851</a>, <a href=\"#/G5342/5342\">G5342</a>, <a href=\"#/G5409/5409\">G5409</a>, <a href=\"#/G5411/5411\">G5411</a>, <a href=\"#/G5412/5412\">G5412</a>, <a href=\"#/G5413/5413\">G5413</a>, <a href=\"#/G5414/5414\">G5414</a>"}]}